# Nomad Hotels - Project Architecture

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15 with App Router (SSR for SEO)
- Chakra UI v3 with official snippets (@chakra-ui/cli)
- TypeScript strict mode
- pnpm package manager
- Biome for linting + formatting
- Deploy on Vercel

## Folder Structure

## File Naming Conventions
- Components: PascalCase (HeroSection.tsx)
- Files/folders: kebab-case (hotel-list.ts)
- Hooks: camelCase starting with 'use' (useHotelData.ts)
- Types: PascalCase (HotelListProps.ts)
- Constants: SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE (API_ENDPOINTS.ts)

## Import Standards
- Use @/ alias for all internal imports
- Use named exports for components
- Group imports: React, libraries, internal
